bluej.codecoverage.utils.serial

Class Coverage

  • java.lang.Object
    • bluej.codecoverage.utils.serial.Coverage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CoverageClass, CoverageMethod, CoveragePackage

    public abstract class Coverage
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents the common elements of all code coverage elements.

    A default Constructor is provided due to the large number of parameters required, as well as serialization.

    Author:
    Ian

    • Constructor Detail

      • Coverage

        protected Coverage(java.lang.String name,
        CoverageCounter lineCoverage,
        CoverageCounter methodCoverage,
        CoverageCounter branchCoverage,
        CoverageCounter classCoverage)
        Fills in all the coverage information that is shared between the different types.
        Parameters:
        name - name associated with the coverage information.
        lineCoverage - code coverage results for individual lines
        methodCoverage - code coverage results for all methods enclosed by this Coverage object.
        branchCoverage - code coverage results for all branches enclosed by this Coverage object.
        classCoverage - code coverage results for all classes enclosed by this Coverage object.
